	<h2>Free Hearing Tests</h2>

	<p>Peninsula hearing tests are <strong>free of charge</strong> and can be carried out  at our fully equipped centre in Teignmouth, Devon. If you prefer, we can test your hearing in the comfort of your own home &ndash; we offer a home visiting service across Devon and Somerset including Exeter, Torquay, Paignton, Newton Abbot, Exmouth, Plymouth, Taunton and surrounding towns.</p>

	<p>Selecting the correct hearing aids depends on many factors, including the degree of hearing loss, lifestyle, personal preference, and your budget. Our expert, unbiased advice backed up by the very best aftercare service ensures maximum customer satisfaction.</p>

	<p>Initial consultation to fitting for custom made instruments is usually as little as 2 weeks. For some open fit hearing aids, a next day fitting is possible.</p>

	<p>Please <a href="contact-devon-hearing-centre">contact us today to arrange your free hearing test</a>.</p>

